<title>USA: San Juan Trust sets $0.42 special payout.</title>
<headline>San Juan Trust sets $0.42 special payout.</headline>
<dateline>FORT WORTH, Texas 1996-09-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>Bank One Texas, the trustee of San Juan Basin Royalty Trust, said on Wednesday it would distribute a $0.42 per share special dividend on October 15 to shareholders of record as of September 30.</p>
<p>The payout is a result of the settlement of litigation between the trustee and Meridian Oil Inc, now known as Burlington Resources Inc, the company said.</p>
<p>In the settlement, Burlington agreed to pay $19.75 million in cash and to provide certain credits related to the lease operating expenses and gas gathering and processing charges.</p>
